<section id="about">
<h2>About</h2>
<p>Melted Essence began from a love of cozy spaces and the belief that scent can anchor us in the present moment. Every candle is a quiet reminder to slow down, light up, and find peace in the simple things.</p>
<p>Each batch is hand-poured with care, using eco-friendly soy wax, lead-free wicks, and phthalate-free fragrance oils. Our goal is to craft scents that ground your soul and elevate your home.</p>
</section>


